2. U7 Chit8 E-hng
U7 chit8 jit8 tui3 hak8-hau7 tng2-lai5 khoaN3-kiN3 kau3-hoe7 u7 kia3 1 pun2 thoan5-to7 sio2-chheh lai5, chit8 jit8 e5 kong-kho3 liau2, chiu7 cheng7-cheng7 theh8 khi2 lai5 thak8, chiu7 si7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 seng5-sit8 e5 jin7-choe7. Hit lang5 un2-tang3 lau5 bak8-sai2 e5 hoe2-kai2, goa2 bak8-chiu kheh-kheh chim-chiok siuN7, sui-jian5 si7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, iau2-ku2 ho2-taN2 ti7 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 kan-cheng3 i ke3-khi3 kian3-siau3 e5 sou2 choe3, che chiaN3 ti7 chin-sit8 ti7 Siong7-te3 bin7-cheng5 liong5-sim e5 ko3-pek8, an2-ni tiam7-tiam7 siuN7 chit8 tiam2-cheng. Am3-si5 10 tiam2 e5 si5, hut-jian5 Siong7-te3 e5 kng chio3 goa2, hou7 goa2 khoaN3 chhut pun2-sin e5 tang7 choe7, Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 goa2 e5 pang5-keng, tui3 chhut-si3 kau3-taN, it-chhe3 e5 choe7 long2 tak8 tiau5 sia2 beng5 ti7 goa2 e5 bak8-cheng5, chit e5 choe7 e5 tang7-taN3 tui3 i2-teng2 ka7 goa2 ap-to2 loh8 chong2-phou teng2. Goa2 khau3 chhut-lai5, bak8-sai2 na2 chui2-chhiang5 chhe7-chhe7 to3, ui7-tioh8 thang kiaN e5 choe7 kap liong5-sim e5 chu7-chek, kha chhiu2 long2 ba5, choan5-sin long2 chhoah, kam2-kak tui3 thau5-khak teng2 kau3 kha-toe2 choan5-sin to si7 choe7, chin si7 phaiN2 khoaN3 e5 si-the2.
“Tui3 kha-toe2 kau3 thau5-khak teng2 bo5 chit8 toe3 ho2-bah; long2 si7 siong-chhui3.” (I2-sai3-a 1:6) Siu7 lang5 o-lo2 ho2 kiaN2 e5 si5, chiu7 kam2-kak na2 chhin-chhiuN7 siu7 thoa kau3 Siong7-te3 bin7-cheng5, ui7 choe7 e5 heng5-hoat8, siu7 soan-ko3 eng2-oan2 biat8-bo5 e5. Peh8-chhat8, thau-theh8, lai7-sim e5 cheng5-iok8, hu-eng5, kiau-ngou7, ke2-ho2, oan3-tou3, saN-chiN teng2 kong2 be7 chin7, poaN3-mi5 khi2-lai5 tui3 thang-a2 khoaN3 thiN-teng2 e5 geh8, iN5-iN5 e5 geh8-kng, ti7 kim-mi5 si7 kou5 bak8-sai2 choe7 e5 piau2-hian7. Goa2 che7 teh siuN7, chit e5 chiah-nih8 tang7 choe7 e5 lang5 iau2 oah8 kau3 kin-a2-jit8, bo5 si2 iau2 oah8 teh si7 ka3-si7; goa2 e5 choe7 teh chiu3-chou2 goa2. Na7 siuN7 tioh8 goa2 kau3-taN 2-3 geh8 jit8 tak8 am3 thak8 Seng3-keng chiu3-chou2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, ia7 khi3 kau3-hoe7 si7 siuN7 beh pian7-pok8, chiu7 sim-koaN giong7 beh piak-lih8 khia7 be7 tiau5 toe7. Tui3 an2-ni goa2 te7-it; tui3 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 Siong7-te3 ki5-to2. “ThiN-toe7 na7 u7 Siong7-te3, kiu5 Li2 kiu3 goa2 chit e5 tang7 choe7 e5 lang5” Te 2: koat-sim tui3 kau3-hoe7 piau2 ui5-ham7, Chiu7 lau5 bak8-sai2 kiah8 pit theh8 kng2-choa2 lai5 sia2 chham3-hoe2 liok8, thiN-kng chiu7 theh8 khi3 kau3-hoe7, soe3 keng kau3-hoe7 an2-chun2 sim-giam5 thih-mng5 e5 kaN-gak8, kong2 beng5 lai5-i3, chiong chham3-hoe2-liok8 theh8 hou7 bok8-su, Kiat-tian5 bok8-su chiap-tioh8 chiu7 the3 goa2 ki5-to2, hit e5 ki5-to2 oan2-jian5 lui5 tui3 goa2 e5 thau5-khak kong3 loh8-lai5 e5 kiaN-hiaN5.
Tui3 chia khi2 bo5-lun7 khi3 hak8-hau7 a2-si7 tng2-lai5, goa2 long2 aN3-thau5 ki5-to2! Siong7-kho3 e5 si5 ia7 hap8-chhiu2 ti7 toh-teng2, kheh-bak8, lai5 sng3 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7, chiu7 thou2-khui3. Bo5 kap peng5-iu2 kong2 oe7, bo5 chhio3, bo5 ng3-bang7, bo5 lun7 kau3 toh-loh8 to na2-chun2 u7 te7-gek8 e5 mng5 teh ui5 goa2. Chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 ou-am3 tiong teh thou2-khui3, siong5-siong5 hap8-chhiu2 ki5-to2 “Ah! Na7 u7 Siong7-te3, kiu5 Li2 chin2-kiu3 goa2”. Tek8-piat8 hian2-beng5 goa2 si7 ke2 ho2 e5 lang5, tui3 goa2 ka-ki7 kong2 “Li2 chit e5 lang5-bin7 khim5-siu3 e5 sim, chit khoan2 ke2-ho2 e5 lang5 cha2 si2 m7 khah ho2, chit8 e5 hou5-tou5 lang5 ke2 choe3 ho2 lang5 oah8 tiam3 se3-kan siaN2 lou7-eng7?” Tong5-si5 jin7-chin khi3 kau3-hoe7 seng5-siu7 ka3-si7.
“Jia-iam2 ka-ki7 e5 choe7-ok e5, boe7 heng-thong, tok8-tok8 jin7-choe7 lai5 koe2-piN3 e5, beh tit-tioh8 lin5-bin2.” (Chim-gian5 28:13)
3. Siong7-te3 E5 Siann
Ke3 lai5 tak8 jit8 to si7 tim5-tiong7 e5 hoe2-kai2, in-ui7 choe7 e5 chek-hoat8 thau5 kiah8 boe7 khi3, sim-lai7 put-si5 saN kau-chian3. Ti7 chiah e5 jit8-chi2 goa2 cheng7-cheng7 khai-si2 hoe2-kai2, hng7 e5 lang5 eng7 phoe-sin3, kin7 e5 lang5 chhin-sin khi3 kiu5 sia3-bian2, ia7 pi-siong ka-ki7 e5 bo5 iong2-khi3. Tui3 chia khi2 eng7 khiam-sun3, iu-siong thong3-hoe2 e5 sim thak8 Seng3-keng, ki5-kiu5 chin2-kiu3 e5 kng, jiat8-sim thiaN bok8-su e5 oe7, chin7-lat8 lai5 li2-kai2. Chong2-si7 chin2-kiu3 na2 chun2 chin hng7, kau3-hoe7 e5 lang5 khoaN3 goa2 e5 kian-sim thau3-cha2 khi3 soaN-teng2, khui tek8-piat8 e5 ki5-to2-hoe7. Jit8-pun2 Ki-tok kau3-hoe7 e5 Kiat-tian5 bok8-su thiaN Tai7-chhau2 tiuN2-lo2 kong2 khi2 si5-siong5 u7 cho2-thian ki5-to2-hoe7 e5 su7.
