5. Lau5 Bak8-sai2 E5 Soann-kok
Chhiong-moa2 teng5-thau5-siN e5 hoaN-hi2, sim tui5-thiau3, sin-khu khin-sang, khai-si2 ti7 khong3-ia2 ki5-to2, ti7 ho5-piN chan3-bi2 Chu2 khoai3-lok8 e5 seng-oah8, le2-pai3 m7 bat khiam3-sek8, liu5-sim eng7 phou7-a2 ki3 bok8-su e5 kang2-to7, koh chai3 thak8 chiaN5 choe3 pun2-sin e5 seng-oah8, ti7 sin3-giong2 e5 lou7 tit-tioh8 chiok-hok. Khai-si2 tui3 toa7-lang5, hak8-seng, chhu3-piN e5 gin2-na2 thoan5 hok-im, cho3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 lau7-su, chhoa7 tioh8 kui2-na7 chap8 e5 gin2-na2, kau3-hoe7 chin lau7-jiat8. Bo5-lun7 toa7 sio2 kho2-chhi3 ia7 giam5-siu2 seng3 jit8, ti3-i3 Siong7-te3 kap kau3-hoe7 tiong-sim e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8, lai5 cho3 kian3-cheng3, chin ki5-biau7 goa2 e5 hak8-giap8 it-hoat tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 su3-hok, chiu7 chiong chit ho7 hoaN-hi2 e5 sin3-sek po3-ko3 kou3-hiong e5 pe7-bo2. Liong-pit pe7-bo2 kaN2 e7 hoaN-hi2, bo5 phah-sng3 liam5-piN chiap-tioh8 choat8-ian5-chng7 (pe7-kiaN2 choat8-ian5, siu7 koaN2-chhut e5 phoe) “chit-khoan2 m7 ai3 chou2-thoan5 e5 hut8-kau3 khi3 sin3 goa7-kok sin5-beng5 e5 lang5, bo5 pe7 bo5 kiaN2 lah, ka7 goa2 chhut-khi3, m7 kia3 hak8-hui3 hou7 li2 lah”.
It-seng chit chit8-pai2 chiap tioh8 lau7-pe7 e5 choat8-ian5 chng7, chhiu2 theh8 phoe toa3 pang5-keng hau2 khah bo5 lang5 chai, chai3-saN siuN7 lai5 siuN7 khi3, choe3-au7 ti7 Siong7-te3 lai5 koan-sim, “kau3 taN goa2 hoan7-choe7 kiaN5 biat8-bo5 e5 lou7, kau3 te7-gek8 mng5-khau2, taN tit-kiu3; Chu2 Ia5-sou hian3 I e5 siN3-mia7 kiu3-siok8 goa2, goa2 goan7 pang3-sak it-chhe3 ku-te3 Chu2 Ia5-sou”. Chiu7 koat-sim the3-oh8 che7 hoe2-chhia tng2 khi3 kou3-hiong. Ti7 chhia-lai7 it-bi7 kiu5 Siong7-te3 e5 pang-chan7, ki5-to2 na2 chih8-cham7, chiu7 leng2-cheng7 ap-to2 goa2. Hit am3 kiaN-kiaN hiaN5-hiaN5 jip8 chhu3 mng5 kui7 ti7 chong2-phou teng2, tui3 lau7-pe7 kong2 khi2 thau5 kau3 be2 tit-kiu3 e5 kian3-cheng3. 2 tiam2 cheng au7, liau7-siong2 lau7-pe7 beh kiah8 thui5-a2 khi2-lai5 kong3 soa3 koaN2 goa2 chhut-khi3, thau kiah8-thau5 khoaN3 lau7-pe7 e5 bin7, lau7-bu2 che7 ti7 piN-a2 bin7 chin ut-bun7, lau7-pe7 bin7 ang5 kong3-kong3 teh lau5 bak8-sai2. Gek8-choan2! Tui3 Seng3 Sin5 kong2 boe7 chhut thou2-khui3 e5 tai7-to2. “Sia3-bian2 li2! Koh khi3 hak8-hau7 thak8-chheh” bin5-bang7 ia7 bo5 siuN7 e7-thang thiaN tioh8 chit ku3 oe7. Ah! Siong7-te3 si7 thiaN3.
“ThiaN3 pe7-bu2 khah ke3-thau5 ti7 thiaN3 Goa2 e5, boe7 kham-tit ti7 Goa2.” (Ma2-thai3 10:37)
6. Sin3 E5 Cheng-chian3
Hak8-seng kan u7 lang5 the5-khi2 siat-lip8 Ki-tok-kau3 chheng-lian5-hoe7 e5 su7, goa2 u7 jiat8-sim tui3 choe7-choe7 hak8-seng thoan5-to7, chiu7 chu7-chip8 tang5 sin3 e5 peng5-iu2 lai5 seng5-lip8, chheng choe3 “Gak8 lam5 hoe7” hoat-hoe7 sek hit jit8 goa2 tui3 tai7-ke kong2 “choe3 chiaN5 tui7 ia7 oe7 liam5-piN to2, beh hou7 i be7 to2, tek-khak tioh8 ki5-to2, ui7-tioh8 beh chi-chhi5 chit e5 hoe7 goa2 beh chiaN5 choe3 ki5-to2 e5 lang5” goa2 chiu7 ti7 chiau3-siong3 e5 si5 kui7 teh ki5-to2; chham-ka hit e5 chiau3-siong3. Ti7 hak8-hau7 lang5 long2 kong2 goa2 si7 Ki-tok e5 siau2 lang5, thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5 poaN3-tiam2 chit8 tiam2-cheng ku2 ui7-tioh8 200 goa7 lang5 lai5 ki5-to2, koh ti3-i3 thak8 Seng3-keng, am3-si5 ka-ki7 chit8 lang5 khi3 soaN-nih8, ti7 toa7 chhiu7-kha ki5-to2. KoaN5-thiN si5 u7 si5 thng3-theh toa7-siaN ki5-to2 “oh! chi2 u7 chit8 pai2 e5 jin5-seng, Chu2 ah hou7 goa2 chai Li2 e5 tiau3-beng7, ia7 chan7 goa2 e7-tit oan5-chiaN5 hit e5 tiau3-beng7” Thak8 sin3-giong2 e5 chheh choe3 khoai3-lok8, che7 ti7 chhiN-chhau2 teng2 thak8 1 iah8 chiu7 ki5-to2, koh thak8 1 iah8 chiu7 bek8-siong2. Chhim-sin3 kam2-hoa3 goa2 choe3 chhim e5 chheh si7 Chu2 sou2 su3 sin3-giong2 e5 sian-siN. Seng3-keng koh lai5 chiu7-si7 ai3 thak8 chiah e5 chheh, si7 thak8 3 pian3 5 pian3 10 pian3. Hut-lan5-se-su, Oe7-su-le2, Sat-hu-sun-tai7, Keng2-poe7 sou2 tu3 e5 chheh siang7 ho2, chhian-bang7 goa2 ia7 oe7 tit chiau3 an2-ni pang3-sak it-chhe3 lai5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 kap lang5.
“Chheng-khi3 sim-koaN e5 lang5 u7 hok-khi3, in-ui7 in beh khoaN3-kiN3 Siong7-te3.” (Ma2-thai3 5:8)
7. Kap Chit Se3-kan E5 Kau-chian3
Hit ni5 ni5-be2 tong5-kip seng koat-gi7 beh khui bong5-lian5-hoe7 tiuN5-sou2 ti7 chiu2-ka, hoe7-hui3 1 lang5 5 khou, chai7 lai5 tak8 hang7 goa2 long2 kap in tong5-i3, taN goa2 i2-keng ko3-pek8 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 sou2-i2 be7 thang kap in tang5 pou7-tiau, goa2 chiu7 khi2-lai5 tui3 in soan-gian5 “goa2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5, sou2-i2 choat8-tui3 kim3 chiu2” koh “lan2 si7 pe7-bu2 kia3 chiN5 hou7 lan2 thak8-chheh e5, kio3 ge7-toaN3 lai5 lim chiu2 m7 hap8-kai” ka7 in hoan2-tui3, in koh-khah oan3-hin7 Chu2 me7 goa2, u7 lang5 toa7 siu7-khi3 “ka7 siu-li2!” tui3 an3-ni siu7 tong5-hak8 pai5-thek, bo5 lang5 kap goa2 kong2 oe7, thau3 oah8-mia7 e5 mng5 sit8-chai7 oeh8.
Goa2 khi3 kau3-hoe7 kong2 hou7 bok8-su thiaN kap i chham-siong5, choan5 kau3-hoe7 long2 chi-chhi5 goa2 khai-si2 the3 goa2 ki5-to2. Chit8 jit8 goa2 tui3 hak8-hau7 beh tng2-lai5, ti7 lou7-nih8 kan-ta chit8 lang5 tiam7-tiam7 teh kiaN5-lou7, thiaN-kiN3 au7-bin7 u7 peng5-iu2 teh kio3 “Cho2-tin5!” I oa2 lai5 ka7 goa2 kong2 “goa2 chai li2 sin3 Ki-tok sit8-heng5 kim3-chiu2 bo5 jip8 im5-loan7 e5 sia7-hoe7, chong2-si7 goa2 si7 li2 e5 chhin-iu2, ui7-tioh8 li2 kap tong5-hak8 cho3 bo7-a2-sim, sou2-i2 pai3-thok li2 bak8-chiu pang3 kheh-kheh lai5 chhut-sek8 leh, bo5 lim-chiu2, bo5 chhiuN3-koa bo5 iau3-kin2, mai3 ka7 khoaN3 ge7-toaN3 e5 bin7, choe3 li2 tiam7-tiam7 ki5-to2, hit e5 tiuN5-bin7 kiam2-chhai2 oe7 tit-tioh8 chheng-khi3!” goa2 thiaN chit khoan2 un-loan2 tong5-cheng5 e5 oe7 tong3 boe7 tiau5, chiu7 toan3-jian5 kong2 “Li2 e5 oe7 goa2 boe7 thang chan3-seng5, sin3-giong2 si7 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 e5 lou7” peng5-iu2 siu7-khi3 2 lang5 chiu7 li7-piat8, chiu7-si7 kiaN5 pi-siong jin5-seng e5 pun-chhe tiam2, an2-ni goa2 m7 bat suh 1 ki hun, choan-sim chit8-i3 giong2-bong7 Chu2, kun-te3 I.
“Lin2 tioh8 tui3 hit e5 oeh8-mng5 jip8; in-ui7 thau3 kau3 biat8-bo5 e5, hit e5 mng5 khoah, hit e5 lou7 toa7 tiau5, tui3 hia jip8 e5 lang5 choe7. Thau3-kau3 oah8 e5, hit e5 mng5 oeh8, hit e5 lou7 soe3-tiau5, chhe7 tioh8 e5 lang5 chio2.” (Ma2-thai3 7:13:14)
8. The3 Oh8 E5 Koat-i3
Na2 chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 pang3-sak chit se3-kan it-chhe3 e5 ng3-bang7, ki5-sit8 si7 Ki-tok e5 thiaN3-thang3 chhui-pek goa2. Bo5 poaN3 lang5 beh kap goa2 kong2 oe7 chit khoan2 hak8-hau7 seng-oah8 tit8-tit8 bo5 ai3, taN beh chaiN2-iuN7? Chiu7 siuN7 tioh8 kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2, khai-si2 kim3-chiah8 e5-hng tng3 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3, lim-chui2 chiah8 chheng peh hioh8. Khai-si2 thoan3-lian7 nai7-khou2, nai7-pin5, nai7-iau e5 nai7-hoat8 seng-oah8. U7 chit8 e5-hng e5 ki5-to2-hoe7, bo5-i3-tiong an2-ni kian3-cheng3, bok8-su tioh8 chit8 kiaN kong2 “He m7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 lou7”, si7 kong2 “Siong7-te3 si7 chhong3-cho7 thiN toe7 e5 Chu2, u7 pi7-pan7 sou2 su-iau3 e5 mih8” chong2-si7 cheng-sin5 tek e5 khou2-chian3 m7-si7 an2-ni soah, kau3-be2 chiu7 khoan2 heng5-li2, koat-sim the3-oh8, kap Gak8-lam5-hoe7 lang5-sin3 e5 peng5-iu2 saN si5, in long2 che5-siaN ban2-liu5 goa2, chong2-si7 boe7 oe7 chou2-tong3 goa2 choe3-au7 khi3 kau3-hoe7 si5-piat8 bok8-su, bok8-su tioh8 toa7-kiaN.
“Sian-siN, siu7 tioh8 li2 thiaN3 chin toa7, taN goa2 the3 oh8 lah!”
“An2-ni li2 beh chhong3 sim2-mih8?”
“Goa2 beh choe3 thoan5-to7-chia2, thoan5 hok-im kau3 si2.”
“Beh khi3 to2-ui7 thoan5?”
“KiaN5 kau3 hia thoan5 kau3 hia.”
Bok8-su it-hoat kiaN.
“Cho2-tin5 hiaN, chhiaN2 ban7, li2 sou2 choe3 bo5 tu2-ho2, tak8-hang7 su7 tioh8 chiau3 to7-li2, li2 koh kui2 geh8-jit8 chiu7 pit-giap8.”
“Si7!”
“Li2 tioh8 thak8 hou7 pit-giap8, theng3-hau7 1 ni5, hit tiong-kan goa2 the3 li2 siat-hoat jip8 Sin5-hak8-hau7, ti7 hia thak8 liau2 li2 thang choe3 chin ho2 e5 thoan5-kau3-su.” Goa2 thau5-khak chhih-chhih in3 kong2 “An2-ni ho2!”
9. Keng-ke3 Lau5 Bak8-sai2 E5 Soann-kok
Kai-chai3 koh lau5 ti7 hak8-hau7, chong2-si7 iau2 chit kui2 geh8-jit8 si7 hoan5-bun7 kap ki5-to2 e5 seng-oah8, na2 ki5-to2 sim na2 kam2-kak Chu2 Ia5-sou teh chio goa2 choe3 thoan5-to7-chai2. Hak8-hau7 sun7-su7 pit-giap8, u7 thau5-lou7, u7 ka-teng5, che si7 goa2 ko3-jin5 e5 su7, si7 sio2-su7, khoaN3 bo5 ka-ki7 lai5 kun-te3 Chu2, choe3 thoan5-to7-chia2, in2-chhoa7 choe7-choe7 choe7-jin5 jip8 thian-kok, chiaN3 si7 goa2 choe3 toa7, choe3 sin5-seng3 e5 tiau3-beng7, chong2-si7 goa2 keng2 chit tiau5 lou7, it-teng7 eng2-oan2 siu7 koaN2 chhut, siuN7 kau3 chia chiu7 it-hoat pek-chhiat ki5-to2 “ah! Siong7-te3 ah, ka3-si7 goa2 sou2 tioh8 kiaN5 e5 lou7, in2-chhoa7 goa2, lin5-bin2 goa2 chit8 e5 loan2-jiok8 e5 lang5, goa2 chiong chit e5 seng-khu leng5-hun5 long2 hian3 hou7 Chu2!” Tak8 mi5 ti7 bo5 lang5 chheng-cheng7 e5 sou2-chai7, pek-chhiat an2-ni ki5-to2.
Hak8-hau7 pit-giap8, tng2-lai5 kou3-hiong, i2-goa7 hou7 goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 Chu2 e5 seng3-chhiu2, si7 lau7-bu2 khi2-siau2. Goan5-in tai7-khai3 in-ui7 lau7-pe7 e5 houN3-chiu2, bo5 cheng3-keng, chu7-jian5 goa2 u7 khan3-hou7 e5 chek-jim7. U7 si5 kui le2-pai3 long2 bo5 chiah8, bih tiam3 phoe7-lai7 khau3, u7 si5 chiu7 toa7-loan7, kiah8 chhai3-to tui beh thai5 tau3 kha-chhiu2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, khoaN3 tioh8 sim-koaN phok8-phok8 chheng2, si5-khek to boe7 thang pang3-sang. U7-si5 mi5-si5 chiah chhe7 bo5 lau7-bu2 e5 chong-chek, chiu7 si3-koe3 chhe7, chiah ti7 soaN-nih8 chhe7 tioh8 i ti7 hia khau3, chiah chhoa7 i tng2-lai5. Koh u7 si5 chhe7 long2 bo5, siuN7 kong2 kaN2 si7 tng2-khi3 au7-thau5 chhu3, chiu7 theh8 ioh8-kan chau2 8 kong-li2. Lou7-tiong tu2-ho2 tiong3 toa7-chui2, kio5 lau5-khi3, goa2 chiu7 thng3 saN pak8 toa3 thau5-khak koat si2 e5 kak-ngou7 siu5 ke3 ho5, kau3 ui7 lau7-bu2 ko2-jian5 ti7 hia, tiam7-tiam7 che7, goa2 ka7 i kio3 ia7 long2 bo5 in3! M7 chiah8, ioh8-kan siak hou7 phoa3. U7 si5 theh8 he2-chha5 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 beh pang3-he2, hou7 lang5 sim chin put-an, sit8-chai7 kau3-giah8 thang pi-siong.
I-ioh8 bo5 kong-hau7, goa2 chiu7 ki5-kiu5 Siong7-te3. Lau7-pe7 u7 chhiaN2 toe7-li2-su lai5 khoaN3, kong2 si7 hit keng sin khi2 e5 chau3-kha soah-tioh8, sou2-i2 ti7 hit e5 chiu-ui5 sio-hiuN liam7-keng. Goa2 chiu7 khai-si2 jiat8-sim ki5-to2, ti3-i3 gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng ai3 chai Chu2 chaiN2-iuN7 i-ti7 piN7-lang5, chaiN2-iuN7 koaN2-kui2 i cheng-sin5 piN7, koh hit tiap8 khi2, e5-hng si5 chu7-chip8 chheng-lian5 lang5 khai-si2 chu7-hoe7, tong5-si5 chu7-chip8 chng lai7 e5 gin2-a2 khai-si2 Chu2-jit8-oh8, tit-tioh8 Chu2 e5 su3-hok, chng-lai7 e5 gin2-na2 bo5 chit8 e5 bo5 lai5, lian5 bio7-nih8 e5 gin2-na2 ia7 lai5, tian-to3 ma5-hoan5. Hoe7-tiuN5 ti7 chhng-khou3, eng7 chheh-pau choe3 i2-a2, chheng-lian5 si7 am3-si5 ti7 soaN-teng2 tiam2-teng lai5 chu7-hoe7, u7 chit8 e5 hiaN-ti7 ti7 hoe7-tiong bak8-chiu pian3-sek, chhut kiN5-iN7 e5 siaN hoat-choh, chiu7 si7 iuN5-hin5-cheng3, goan2 chiu7 ui7 chit e5 hiaN-ti7 ki5-to2.
Ui7-tioh8 lau7-bu2 kap chit e5 hiaN-ti7 chin7-lat8 e5 ki5-to2, ia7 long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 sin5-jiah. Che long2 si7 ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 bo5 chheng-khi3. Cho2-thian ki5-to2 liam7 choe7-choe7 lang5 e5 mia5 the3 in ki5-to2. Te7-it; si7 chit e5 iuN5-hin5 e5 hiaN-ti7, te7-ji7: si7 ui7-tioh8 lau7-bu2. I u7 koh khai-si2 jiat8-sim tui3 toa7-lang5 thoan5-to7, chng-nih8 toa7 hok8-heng, gin2-na2 khoaN3 tioh8 goa2 chiu7 kiah8-chhiu2 hoah “Eng-e3 ban7-soe3” chong2-si7 u7 e5 in-ui7 sin3 goa7-kok sin5 e5 li2-iu5 hou7 hak8-hau7 e5 lau7-su phah, koh u7 e5 in-ui7 sin3 Ki-tok siu7 pe7-bu2 chek-pi7, m7 chun2 khi3 hak8-hau7. Goa2 ia7 kam2-kak m7 thang ku2-tng5 toa3 chia, chiu7 khai-si2 chun2-pi7 jip8 Sin5-hak8-hau7. “Lai5 te3 goa2, goa2 beh hou7 lin2 tit-tioh8 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 tho2-hi5 e5.” (Ma2-thai3 4:19)
10. Jip8 Sin5 Hak8-hau7
Tui3 Kiat-tian5 bok8-su e5 ho2-i3 e7 thang jip8 Sin5 hak8-hau7, chong2-si7 u7 chit8 e5 lan5-koan chiu7-si7 chhin-chhek e5 hoan2-tui3. Lau7-pe7 am3-am3 pai3-thok chhin-chhek iu2-lek8 e5 i-seng beh khou2-khng3 goa2. U7 chit8 jit8 chhe lang5 kio3 goa2 khi3, chek-si5 khai-si2 chham-siong5 chiong-sin e5 su7.
“Li2 si7 toa7 kiaN2, lau7-bu2 u7 hit khoan2 cheng-sin5-piN7, lau7-pe7 kin7-lai5 sim-chong7 ia7 m7 ho2, koh lin2 sio2-ti7 bo5 ku2 tioh8 khi3 choe3 peng, li2 tek-khak tioh8 hok8-sai7 pe7-bu2, lai5 seng5-chiap ke-giap8, sou2-i2 tioh8 kiat-hun.”
Goa2 in3 kong2 “Boe7 eng7-tit, chit e5 sin-khu, leng5-hun5 long2 hian3 hou7 Ki-tok, goa2 tioh8 choe3 thoan5-to7-chia2.”
I-seng kong2 “Phoa3-piN7 e5 si5 sim2-mih8 lang5 beh khoaN3-kou3?”
“Siong7-te3 teh khoaN3-kou3.”
“Khun3-lan5 e5 si5, sim2-mih8 lang5 chiN5 hou7 li2?”
“Khun3-lan5 e5 si5 Siong7-te3 e7 pang-chan7 goa2.”
“Bo5 chai5-san2, li2 e5 Siong7-te3 kiam2 oe7 ka7 li2 po2-cheng3?”
“Oe7! I oe7 ka7 goa2 pi7-pan7 sou2 khiam3-eng7 e5.” I-seng khoaN3-phoa3 lah! Kong2 chit khoan2 oe7 it-seng thau5 chit8 pai2 thiaN-kiN3, Bok8-hou7 in hau7-siN e5 sin3-giong2 tam5 thong chng long2 chai, chiaN5 choe3 chng-nih8 chhut-mia5 oe7-te5. Chong2-si7 m7 si7 an2-ni soah, koh lai5 chiu7-si7 khui ka-chok8 hoe7-gi7. U7 pian7-hou7-su7, u7 hak8-hau7 e5 lau7-su, u7 choh-sit lang5, ia7 u7 seng-li2 lang5, chit8 e5-hng tai7-ke long2 chiau5 kau3, goa2 che7 ti7 siang7 be2 ui7, chit8 e5 chit8 e5 to si7 jiat8 kun2-kun2 e5 kau3-hun3, thau5 kau3 be2 goa2 long2 thau5-khak chhih-chhih teh thiaN. Tak8 e5 to si7 kong2:
“Ki-tok-kau3 kiam2 si7 ka3 lang5 put-hau3 e5 chong-kau3 na7 hit ho7 chong-kau3 m7 thang sin3, na7-si7 ka3-si7 iu2-hau3, chiu7 li2 tioh8 toa3 chhu3-nih heng-hau3 pe7-bu2, seng5-chiap ka-giap8 chiah tioh8.” Goa2 in3 kong2 “Ki-tok-kau3 si7 ka3-si7 lang5 iu2-hau3, chong2-si7 goa2 siu7 tiau3 tioh8 khi3 choe3 thoan5-to7-chia2, goa2 na7 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3, chiu7 I oe7 khoaN3-kou3 goa2 e5 ka-teng5, Siong7-te3 u7 choe3 ho2 e5 an-pai5, lau7-bu2 e5 piN7 ia7 oe7 ho2, bian2 chiN5, bian2 chai5-san2, chi2-u7 chit8 seng-khu chiu7 ho2, chhiaN2 iong5-un2 goa2 khi3.” An2-ni kui2 na7 pai2, kau3-be2 tai7-ke long2 khoaN3-phoa3, phau7 tioh8 sit-bang7 kap siu7-khi3, chin am3 chiah tng2-khi3, goa2 chiu7 koaN7 chit8 e5 heng5-li2 khi3 Sin5-hak8-hau7.
“In-ui7 pe7-bu2 li7-khui goa2. Ia5-ho5-hoa beh siu-liu5 goa2.” (Si-phian 27:10)
11. Siong7-te3 E5 Sim-su
Jip8 Sin5-hak8-hau7 thang hak8-sip8 choe7-choe7 hang7, chi2 u7 chit8 hang7 goa2 bo5 be7 ki3-tit, chiu7-si7 lau7-bu2 e5 phoa3-piN7, cha2, am3 jiat8-sim teh ki5-to2, chong2-si7 long2 bo5 thiaN tioh8 ho2 e5 siau-sit, che si7 tui3 goa2 e5 bo5 kau3-giah8 jiat8-sim, sou2-i2 ki5-to2 bo5 tit-tioh8 chiap-lap8, tak8 e5-hng kim3-chiah8, thng3 chhiah-kha chhut-khi3 Sin5-hou7 e5 ke-lou7, lou7-piN pou3-to7, sui-jian5 loh8-seh, iau2-ku2 chin-choe7 lang5 kiah8 hou7-soaN3 khia7 teh thiaN. Tng2-lai5 hak8-liau5 beh khun3, chong2-si7 thong-mi5 kau3 thiN-kng kha long2 be7 sio. An2-ni iau2-ku2 be7 thang thiaN-kiN3 ho2 e5 sin3-sek, siuN7 kong2 che si7 in-ui7 goa2 e5 jiok8-the2 su-iok8 bo5 chheng-khi3, chiu7 ti7 chheh-tu5 au7 khng3 chit8 ki chhe5-a2, na7 sim-lai7 u7 phaiN2 liam7-thau5 jip8-lai5 chiu7 kiah8 khi2-lai5 kong3 thau5-khak hoan2-hoe2 ki5-to2.
Chit si5 siu7 chi2-si7 chit8 hang7 choe7, chiu7-si7 siuN7 khi2 goa2 10 he3 e5 si5 ti7 chng-nih e5 tiam2-a2 thau-theh8 1 te3 sap-bun5, tiam3-chu2 m7 ai3 chhap gin2-na2 1, 2 chiam e5 boe2-be7, chin m7 kam-goan7, tng-tan2 i bo5 chu3-i3 chiu7 ka7 thau-theh8 1 te3 5 chiam chiN5 e5 sap-bun5, chek-si5 sia2 phoe lok 1 kak-gun5 e5 iu5-phio3 kia3 tng2-khi3 ka7 tiam3-chu2 sia7 choe7, tiam3-chu2 chiap tioh8 phoe, kam2-kak oah8 Ki-tok e5 hok-im, chiong phoe theh8 khi3 hou7 lau7-pe7 khoaN3, lau7-pe7 gou7-kai2 si7 tiam3-chu2 teh bu2-jiok8 i chin siu7-khi3, te7 2 pai2 chiap tioh8 choat8-ian5 chng7, “choe3 chhat8 e5 put-hau3 kiaN2, pe7-bu2 e5 bin7 hou7 li2 kou5 noa7-thou5, m7 chun2 li2 ka7 goa2 tng2-lai5, tui3 chia pe7, kiaN2 choat8-ian5!” chit tiuN phoe hou7 goa2 sin-khu gi7-gi7 chhoah.
Lang5 sou2 ia7 e5 si7 sim2-mih8, i ia7 beh siu hit ho7.” (Ka-liap8-thai3 6:7) Chu2 e5 oe7 si7 chin, goa2 chit e5 choe7-jin5 eng-kai siu7 choe7 e5 heng5-hoat8.
Kau3 hioh-joah8 e5 si5, sui5 lang5 long2 chin hoaN-hi2 beh chhut-khi3 ha7-kui3 thoan5-to7, goa2 siuN7 beh khi3 Su3-kok e5 nai7-piN7-to2 soe2 piN7-lang5 e5 kha, khi3 kau3 Ko-chheng5 chiah chai m7-chun2 jip8 to2, chiu7 peh chiuN7 Pat-to2 e5 koan5 soaN-teng2, chhu than2-a2 ti7 hia kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2 3 jit8 ku2. Lam2 Seng3-keng siuN7 khi2 goa2 e5 phaiN2-mia7 soa3 khau3 khi2-lai5, khau3 kau3 bak8-sai2 tih tam5 Seng3-keng, ou-a pi-siong e5 siaN i2-goa7 long2 bo5 thiaN-kiN3 sim2-mih8, siuN7 beh toa3 chia kim3-chiah8 hou7 i si2, chong2-si7 be7 kham-tit iau chiu7 loh8 soaN, siuN7 kau3 ka-ki7 khek-ki2 sim e5 nng2-chiaN2 kau3-giah8 kian3-siau3.
Sin-khu bo5 poaN3-sian2 chiu7 khi3 tng3-tiam3 beh tng3 si5-pio2 kap sou2 u7 e5 mih8, in-ui7 bo5 po2-cheng3-jin5 tng3-tiam3 m7 chhap goa2, chiu7 hap8 chhiu2 ai-kiu5 koe3-lou7 lang5 ka7 goa2 boe2 sou2 u7 e5 mih8, tit-tioh8 5 khou-gun5, tui3 hia che7 chun5 khi3 Tai7-hun koan7 e5 Cho3-ho7-koan7, sun7 hai2-hoaN7 na2 kiaN5 na2 pou3-to7 khi3 kiong-kia7 tiam3 bou2 kau3-hoe7 lai5 pang-chan7 thoan5-to7, tak8-jit8 tak8 am3 chhiah-kha pou3-to7, tit-tioh8 choe7-choe7 lang5 hoaN-hi2 thiaN. 2 ko3-geh8 e5 hong7-su7 kiat-sok, ti7 sang3-piat8-hoe7 hit am3, tui3 tiuN2-lo2 tit-tioh8 chin ho2 e5 bian2-le7 kap kim chit8 hong, au7-lai5 thiah-khui khoaN3 u7 200 khou. Hak8-liau5 e5 chiah8-hui3 1 geh8 jit8 16 khou, chiah toa7 tiau5 e5 chiN5, chin-chiaN3 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-su3, tng2 lai5 Sin5 hak8-hau7 chiu7 chiong toa7-poaN3 e5 chiN5 pun hou7 song3-hiong e5 tong5-hak8, kiong-kia7 e5 iu2-lek8 chia2 chu7-chip8 beh chou2-chit “Cho2-tin5 hou7-oan7 hoe7” goa2 ka7 in si5 the3, in-ui7 “Siong7-te3 i2-goa7 goa2 bo5 beh oa2-kho3 sim2-mih8”.
Goa2 tng2-lai5 Sin5-hak8-hau7 ia7 bo5 tit-tioh8 lau7-bu2 piN7 ho2 e5 siau-sit, na7 chiau3 an2-ni khi3, chiu7 goa2 si7 chit8 e5 peh8-chhat8 e5, chhin-chok8-hoe7 e5 sek-siong7, goa2 e5 kian3-cheng3 “goa2 na7 kun-te3 Ia5-sou, Chu2 Ia5-sou tek-khak oe7 i-ho2 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2” chit ku3 oe7 khou2-chhou2 goa2 e5 sim, goa2 chiu7 tui3 hau7-tiuN2 kong2 beng5; goa2 beh the3-oh8, koat-sim beh sia2-sin3 thoan5-to7 kap ki5-to2. Mai2-ia-su sian-siN pho7 goa2 e5 am7-kun2 lau5 bak8-sai2 kong2 “Cho2-tin5 kun, li2 tioh8 ke3-siok8 thak8-chheh, Ho7-chhoan-kun hiah-nih8 siu7 tiong7-iong7 si7 tui3 i u7 chhut-lat8 thak8, li2 na7 chhut-lat8 thak8 ia7 beh an2-ni siu7 tiong7-iong7 chit ho7 e5 un-cheng5 goa2 eng2-oan2 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit. (Myers phok-su7 si7 Ho7-chhoan sian-siN e5 un-su).
Chhiau-oat8 gi7-li2 jin5-cheng5, goa2 tui3 Sin5-hak8-hau7 the3-oh8, siuN7 kong2 lau7-bu2 piN7 ho2 liau2-au7, tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2 kaN2 oe7 thang koh thak8 Sin5-hak8.
12. Ki5-to2 E5 Lang5
